{
  "text": "Lung cancer is one of the most common and deadly tumors in the world. From 1995 to 2009, 5-year overall survival of lung cancer patients remains as low as 20 % in developed and developing countries [CITATION_1] . Clinical data show that over 90 % of the deaths of patients with lung cancer are direct or indirect consequence of cancer invasion and metastasis [CITATION_2] .",
